description:
Coronavirus pandemic. Public safety. Vaccine mandates. Freedom of conscience. Do these hot topics have any connection with the coming "mark of the beast” (see Revelation 13:16,17; 19:20)? Secular people, and especially Christians, are pondering these issues worldwide. Do vaccine mandates, which can affect a person’s ability to earn an income (if they don’t comply), foreshadow the approaching time when “no man can buy or sell, save he that has the mark”? Steve Wohlberg offers compelling insights about this raging controversy from the Word of God.
